{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A short walking simulator where you can change environment lighting with the press of a button using the real-time lighting of Unreal Engine 5, where secrets may be revealed by the light or the dark.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Optional paths may hold secret rooms and bits of lore. If a path looks scary, it can usually be avoided if you just want to relax. There is no combat or HUD. No puzzle-solving is required to complete the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The radio  is your tool to change the world lighting, and indicates the current lighting state. A tuner can catch stray signals in some areas, and you might hear music, or possibly other sounds hidden in the static...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274380/extras/1.png?t=1728706806\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274380/extras/2.png?t=1728706806\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The minimal story is mostly told through environment details. There will be a few different endings depending on your actions. But the main focus is to simply enjoy the atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Please enjoy your stay in the Drift Halls.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274380/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728706806","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274380/page.bg.jpg?t=1728706806","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274380/9edfe5e0a17ca37683f4977e784b3808b85f08ed/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728706806","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274380/9edfe5e0a17ca37683f4977e784b3808b85f08ed/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728706806","categories":